annotationA: Splicing factor 3A subunit 3; Probable subunit of a splicing factor complex required for 'A' complex assembly formed by the stable binding of U2 snRNP to the branchpoint sequence (BPS) in pre-mRNA (By similarity). Involved in male fertility; Belongs to the SF3A3 family
annotationB: Probable small nuclear ribonucleoprotein E; Associated with the spliceosome snRNP U1, U2, U4/U6 and U5
